data.description: **BACK ON MARKET AT NO FAULT OF SELLER** Welcome Home to this amazing 4 bd home  in the desirable Summerhaven community and award winning DDII school district. Beautifully tiled foyer and arched doorways will greet you as you walk in.   New LVT in kitchen that boasts stainless steel appliances and opens to spacious living room with gas log fireplace. The open concept kitchen/living room space leaves ample room for entertaining family and friends.  Upstairs you will find all 4 bedrooms and large laundry room. Home has tons of storage throughout. HVAC unit upstairs replaced 2022 and downstairs replaced 2020. Roof replaced 2021. Enjoy all the amenities that Summerhaven has to offer,including a community pool with a pavilion, parks, and walking/jogging trails, and new security license plate reader at entrances. This home is conveniently located just a short 10 minute drive from Downtown Summerville, where you will find local shopping, dining and entertainment options. As well as a short commute to Volvo, Mercedes, Cummings and Boeing Ladson facilities. Ring doorbell camera included. **MOTIVATED SELLER BRING US AN OFFER ** Seller is offering a one year home warranty with acceptable offer.
